T*
(gates, storage transitions, runtime controls, emissions interaction, and release governance for) Tj
T*
(the private layer. The writing model is intentionally deterministic: every major claim either) Tj
T*
(maps to an active code path, an active constant, or a published operational control[^1][^12].) Tj
